        including participating in interviews, book signings, and other promotional activities as
        reasonably requested by Publisher.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>c.</strong>Author grants Publisher the right to use excerpts from the Book for
        promotional purposes, both online and offline.
      </p>

      <h2>Book Launch and Release Date</h2>
